        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Apple Intelligence 未来或会收费，外媒：或将采用月费制</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/03/apple-intelligence-4/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-intelligence-4</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/03/apple-intelligence-4/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 11:00:33 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple Intelligence]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1247561</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Apple 可能计划未来对其 AI 服务 Apple Intelligence 进行收费，以增加公司收入来源和减少对硬件销售的依赖。Bloomberg 记者 Mark Gurman 报道指 Apple 的长期计划包括向用户收费以使用更多 AI 功能。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Apple Intelligence 在上个月的全球开发者大会（WWDC）中亮相，功能包括 ChatGPT 整合、文本校对和重写工具、新的 Siri 功能，以及生成图像和表情符号等。Apple Intelligence 将于今年秋季联同 iOS 18、iPadOS 18 和 macOS Sequoia 作业系统以测试版形式推出。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><strong> </strong></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">根据 Bloomberg 的报导，Apple 可能会推出一个名为 Apple Intelligence+ 的月度付费服务，将与 Apple 的其他数码产品如 iCloud Plus、Apple TV Plus 和 Apple Fitness Plus 采取相似的模式。订阅服务不只可以让 Apple 从其庞大的 iPhone 用户基础中获得更多收益，更可以补充因全球智能手机出货量下滑带来的收入损失。虽然市场在 2024 年开始复苏，但根据国际数据公司（IDC）的数据，智能手机的总出货量仍未达到以往水平。</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.cnet.com/tech/mobile/apple-intelligence-may-eventually-cost-you/">Cnet</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/02/apple-intelligence-ai-paid/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple 传参照 iCloud+ 做法，部分 Apple Intelligence 功能将需要额外收费</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/01/gurman-apple-intelligence-coming-to-vision-pro/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">《彭博》爆料 Apple Intelligence   将登陆 Vision Pro 但 HomePod 不获支援</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/22/apple-intelligence-europe-delay/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple Intelligence 欧盟延期推出　受「数码市场法案」影响今年内不会提供</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/03/apple-intelligence-4/ai/">Apple Intelligence 未来或会收费，外媒：或将采用月费制</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/03/apple-intelligence-4/ai/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Samsung Galaxy Unpacked 传言大集合　6 个预计公布重点</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/03/samsung-galaxy-unpacked-4/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=samsung-galaxy-unpacked-4</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/03/samsung-galaxy-unpacked-4/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 09:00:08 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[潮流手表]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[音乐耳机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Galaxy Buds3]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Galaxy Buds3 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Galaxy Ring]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Galaxy Unpacked]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Galaxy Watch 7]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Galaxy Watch Ultra]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Galaxy Z Flip6]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Galaxy Z Fold6]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Samsung Galaxy Z Fold]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1247509</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Samsung 即将于香港时间 7 月 10 日晚上 9 点于法国巴黎举行 Galaxy Unpacked 发布会。随著  Galaxy Unpacked 日子渐近，各大传媒估计发布会有甚么新产品，现在就让小编分享一下外间有甚么传言吧！</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247512 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Galaxy Unpacked 发布会</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Galaxy Z Fold6、Z Flip6 新机</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">有外媒表示，是次 Galaxy Unpacked 发布会的主角将会是新折机 Galaxy Z Fold6 与 Z Flip6。知名爆料者 Evan Blass 预料 Galaxy Z Fold6 会有浅灰、深蓝与粉红三色，Galaxy Z Flip6 则会有浅灰、水蓝、鹅黄与薄荷绿四色。规格方面，Galaxy Z Fold 6 和 Z Flip 6 会采用与 S24 系列相同的 Qualcomm Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 处理器。暂时未知 Samsung 折机处理器与相机是否会与 S24 系列相同，但 Samsung 曾证实将为折机推出更强大的 Galaxy AI 体验，值得期待一下。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247535 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-18-694x387.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="387" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-18-694x387.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-18.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Galaxy Z Fold6（图片来源：<a href="https://www.t3.com/news/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-6-and-z-flip-6-look-great-in-leaked-official-cases">t3</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247534 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-17-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-17-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-17.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Galaxy Z Flip6（图片来源：<a href="https://www.t3.com/news/samsung-galaxy-z-fold-6-and-z-flip-6-look-great-in-leaked-official-cases">t3</a>）</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Galaxy Watch 7</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">除了新折机外， Samsung 会在发布会上推出新 Galaxy Watch 7 系列，将会推出 40mm 和 44mm 两种尺寸，分别配备 1.3 吋和 1.5 吋萤幕。Galaxy Watch 7 有奶油白、银色和深绿表身搭配上同色波浪设计表带。Galaxy Watch7 拥有 2GB RAM 和 32GB 存储空间，是上代 Galaxy Watch 6 的两倍。电池容量方面，40mm 型号为 300mAh，44mm 型号为 425mAh，与现有型号相同。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247524 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-9-505x580.jpg" alt="" width="505" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-9-505x580.jpg 505w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-9.jpg 784w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 505px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247525 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-10-505x580.jpg" alt="" width="505" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-10-505x580.jpg 505w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-10.jpg 783w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 505px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247528 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-11-504x580.jpg" alt="" width="504" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-11-504x580.jpg 504w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-11.jpg 782w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 504px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400; text-align: center;">▲Galaxy Watch 7 传闻售价：319 欧元（约港币 HK$2,703）（图片来源：<a href="https://www.gsmarena.com/more_renders_of_the_galaxy_unpacked_lineup_leak_ahead_of_launch-news-63490.php">Gsmarena</a>）</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/03/galaxy-watch-ultra-galaxy-watch7-series-price-leaked/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Galaxy Watch Ultra 定价曝光   Galaxy Watch7 系列与上代售价相若</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/02/galaxy-ring-skin-temperature-tracking-snore-detection/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Galaxy Ring 功能预览，提供体温追踪鼻鼾侦测</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/01/galaxy-watch-ultra-leaked/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Galaxy Watch Ultra 产品照曝光，三色表身表带配色选择</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Galaxy Watch Ultra</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">除了全新的 Galaxy Watch 7 系列，Samsung 还会推出全新的 Samsung Galaxy Watch Ultra，期望会与 Apple Watch 高阶款式竞争的 Wear OS 装置。Galaxy Watch7 Ultra 有深灰、银与橙色三种颜式。功能方面， Galaxy Watch Ultra 则与 Galaxy Watch 7 多方面相似，但表壳尺寸增至 47mm，配备 1.5 吋萤幕，并标配 4G 连接，无蓝牙专属型号。电池容量亦有所增加，达到 590mAh，亦有可能同样提供户外活动的高水准追踪功能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247529 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-12-503x580.jpg" alt="" width="503" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-12-503x580.jpg 503w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-12.jpg 781w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 503px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247530 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-13-502x580.jpg" alt="" width="502" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-13-502x580.jpg 502w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-13.jpg 779w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 502px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247531 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-14-505x580.jpg" alt="" width="505" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-14-505x580.jpg 505w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-14.jpg 784w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 505px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400; text-align: center;">▲Galaxy Watch Ultra 传闻售价：699 欧元（约港币 HK$5,931）（图片来源：<a href="https://www.gsmarena.com/more_renders_of_the_galaxy_unpacked_lineup_leak_ahead_of_launch-news-63490.php">Gsmarena</a>）</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Galaxy Ring </strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">Samsung 在 1 月的 S24 发布会上首次展示 Galaxy Ring，惟之后很少提及相关细节。是次发布会终于有望见到其全貌，与 Oura Ring 和 Ultrahuman Ring Air 等竞争产品相比，Galaxy Ring 将提供广泛的健康和健身追踪功能。据传 Galaxy Ring 将有多种尺寸和款式选择，并具备与 Galaxy Watch 类似的健康追踪功能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1247523 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-8-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-8-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-8.jpg 1196w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Galaxy Ring（图片来源：<a href="https://www.techradar.com/health-fitness/samsung-galaxy-ring-teased-at-unpacked-2024-heres-what-it-looks-like">Techradar</a>）</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Galaxy Buds3 与 Galaxy Buds3 Pro</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">Samsung 都是时候更新真无线蓝牙耳机，在发布会上会推出 Galaxy Buds3 及 Galaxy Buds3 Pro，分别都有白、银灰两只颜色。Galaxy Buds3 会用上半入耳式设计，而 Galaxy Buds3 Pro 则会是入耳式设计。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247514 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-2-575x580.jpg" alt="" width="575" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-2-575x580.jpg 575w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-2.jpg 892w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-2-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 575px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247519 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-6-694x517.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="517" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-6-694x517.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-6.jpg 1207w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247520 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-7-694x515.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="515" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-7-694x515.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-7.jpg 1214w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247515 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-3-573x580.jpg" alt="" width="573" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-3-573x580.jpg 573w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-3.jpg 889w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 573px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247517 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-4-694x546.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="546" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-4-694x546.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-4.jpg 1143w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247518 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-5-694x556.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="556" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-5-694x556.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-5.jpg 1124w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Galaxy Buds3 及 Galaxy Buds3 Pro（图片来源：<a href="https://www.androidpolice.com/samsung-july-10-unpacked-event-what-to-expect/">Android Police</a>、<a href="https://www.gsmarena.com/more_renders_of_the_galaxy_unpacked_lineup_leak_ahead_of_launch-news-63490.php">Gsmarena</a>）</p><h2>无平价版 Samsung Galaxy Z Fold</h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">如果用家希望看到平价版的 Samsung Galaxy Z Fold，可能会失望了。据报导，Samsung 一直在研发一款经济实惠的 Galaxy Z Fold，虽然缺少 S Pen 支援等功能，但提供更薄的机身和更大的萤幕。但由于生产延迟至 10 月，其发布可能要推迟到明年。即使平价版 Samsung Galaxy Z Fold 真的会推出，亦可能只会在中国和部分亚洲地区发售。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1247513 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-1-694x459.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="459" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240703at-1-694x459.jpg 694w, https://